  <title>Entry Scale Model with VSA Installation Checklist</title>
  <body>
    <section id="bios"><title>BIOS and iLO Settings</title>
      <p>Ensure that the following BIOS and iLO settings are applied to each baremetal server, with
        the exception of the Deployer.</p>
      <p>
        <table frame="all" rowsep="1" colsep="1" id="table_ckx_rd4_ht">
          <tgroup cols="2">
            <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="25pt"/>
            <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="1*"/>
            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry>&#9744;</entry>
                <entry>Item</entry>
              </row>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry/>
                <entry>Setup the iLO Advanced license in the iLO configuration</entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry/>
                <entry>Switch from UEFI to Legacy BIOS</entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry/>
                <entry>Ensure that the NIC port to be used for PXE insatllation has PXE
                  enabled</entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry/>
                <entry>Ensure that all other NIC ports have PXE disabled</entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry/>
                <entry>Ensure all hardware in the server not directly used by Helion is
                  disabled</entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry/>
                <entry>Disable SR-IOV in the NIC BIOS</entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </table>
      </p>
    </section>
